Something in your nature has set you apart from your fellow 
humans. Where many are content to accept the world around 
them without question, you have probed deeper. From a 
family wealthier than most others, your parents had the 
means to entertain these flights of fancy, allowing you to 
escape hard work except in times of harvest, and instead 
persue a discipline or two of higher thinking.

Perhaps you mastered the wonders of the written word, 
taking opportunity of traveling elves to expand your 
knowledge of literacy. The world of plants, mushroom and 
tinctures may have drawn your eye, or your energies may 
have instead focused on the treatment of the sick and 
injured. Whatever you have bent your mind too, you now 
stand at the beginning of your journey to true mastery of 
your discipline.
